-------------------
SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
-------------------

libcurl
pacman
yajl


-------
TARBALL
-------

The normal installation for a tarball package follows.
$ ./configure
$ make
# make install


---
GIT
---

If you've obtained the source code from git,

$ ./autogen.sh

To generate the configure script. Then follow the tarball installation
procedures.

To cleanup:

$ ./autoclean.sh
